Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信著的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的記憶還沒有完全恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不習慣被人懷疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:01:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經  在這片土地上居住的人都以沉默為美德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多人一向不將關鍵的話說出口  將其默默藏在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原本就是你的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有事件的幕後  都是你在主使吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡爾醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於找到真相了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我孩子們和小櫻的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是拐走孩子們的犯人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有什麼地方搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是擔心那個孩子  才跟在他身後的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指這孩子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿108招密技之一  「超·變身」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好呢  摩可拿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生使用了催眠術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓鎮上的自衛團的人們保護自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,催眠術？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生會使用催眠療法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮上所有人都知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從醫生的出診記錄來看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我又核對了克羅沙姆先生的失蹤名單  所有消失的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失蹤的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在失蹤前的數日內一定都接受了醫生的催眠療法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時  孩子指著天空  可是並沒有鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你給孩子們下了暗示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不會留下足跡的下雪天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟隨著並不存在的鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓孩子們自行失蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份孩子們的失蹤名單就真的值得相信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那方面我可以保證
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:04:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克羅沙姆先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份名單是我親自去每家每戶走訪記下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我同時把國家史書借給這些人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克羅沙姆先生那裡也有那本史書嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要那麼驚訝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是不好辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我們的居然是不利於調查的缺頁書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不得了的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生  不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生把孩子們拐走這件事是騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是騙人的吧  醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我把孩子們聚集起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座城堡裡  有我想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而有能力取出那個的只有孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然為了那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不瞭解那份力量才會說這種蠢話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻的羽毛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了休息的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡曾經是給孩子們提供庇護的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.06,0:06:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會給孩子們帶來不自由的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也必須把大家帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你一個人還是不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我去把小狼君他們叫來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我帶你出城堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這樣看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克羅沙姆先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想得到傳說中的小櫻的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並沒有向任何人提起過  醫生卻知道這是小櫻的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我孩子們和小櫻在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰告訴醫生關於小櫻羽毛的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能在水面上跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  仔細看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  我現在就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這邊也有孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們  快把大家帶出城去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡爾醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君他們在對岸等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把羽毛拿到手的  就是這個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  小櫻小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那根羽毛交出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  這是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:09:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻公主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  把羽毛交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把羽毛交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻公主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  這聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼水會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是用來阻止河水的水門壞掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  黑磷他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑鋼不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼  小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們先走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就這樣不管同伴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼是那種想做到就一定做得到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路出現分岔了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡的秘道我還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一直往前走的話  就可以到達地上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把羽毛交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趁機走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會久一點  但能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能丟下小狼君…不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  再這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾梅洛德公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有一扇圖上沒標出來的暗門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾梅洛德公主告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對公主所說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會有任何懷疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去流速越來越快的話  就沒法渡河了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:14:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咻～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢  小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡爾怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和城堡的命運相同…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是昏過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得真出色呢  小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到羽毛的  是公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾梅洛德公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻可以看得到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金髮的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  什麼都看不到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  一定在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把羽毛還給你真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把孩子們都救回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾梅洛德公主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:04.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人一直在暗中注視著你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「有人一直在暗中注視著你們」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  小櫻能看到艾梅洛德公主  是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是催眠術嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  是羽毛的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  白饅頭應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻公主看見的  或許是艾梅洛德公主的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幽靈嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼怪之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻公主從小時候起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能看到死去的人或生物並與他們交談
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖樓國的人都有這樣的能力嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:17:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.46,0:18:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據我所知  只有神官大人和小櫻公主可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  艾梅洛德公主已經消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子說過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心的事解決了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈就會離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指「成佛」的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她太擔心孩子們了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位金髮公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿也想看看那位公主怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  摩可拿既看不到也感覺不到幽靈嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得到幽靈的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑色的  戴著藍色耳墜的那隻摩可拿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像看過  那個像黑饅頭一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然白饅頭就是沒用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿可是很努力呢  大活躍的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼地方傷到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克羅沙姆先生每天晚上都在尋找孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不告訴我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事用不著宣傳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去這座城鎮的人們  以沉默為美德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是  結果靠我一個人還是沒法找到孩子們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  多虧了那些人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去還是很可疑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們是孩子們的恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要向他們道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫了些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於艾梅洛德公主的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請務必要傳承下去」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「關於艾梅洛德公主的真實傳說」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議的旅人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能夠再次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出發去下一個世界了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.16,0:20:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然把事件解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還有一點不解之謎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:04.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不解之謎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾梅洛德公主跟小櫻所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「有人一直在暗中注視著你們」是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚的地方…還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴卡爾醫生關於小櫻羽毛的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟會是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是同一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關注著的傢伙  以及期望著什麼的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來在我們的旅行中有某人在搞鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個醫生  看來失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠國的羽毛回到玖樓國的公主手上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然能干涉的部分很有限  讓人感到很不甘心…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過只要一想到這是為了獲取力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.56,0:22:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就感到快樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們又踏上旅程了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也繼續進行下一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.71,0:24:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是黑鋼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.61,0:24:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是眾所周知的強悍之士
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.51,0:24:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的世界對我來說很合適哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.81,0:24:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是個人們戴著奇怪面具較量強勁的國家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.91,0:24:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我的對手會是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.21,0:24:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就請繼續期待下去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.81,0:24:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼·年代記
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.01,0:24:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十六話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.11,0:24:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強悍與溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.61,0:24:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的古代神明會讓人期待不已之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.11,0:24:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓我來說！


